</span><span class="mord mathnormal">e</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.01968em;">l</span><span class="mord mathnormal">se</span><span class="mspace"> </span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.01968em;">Bl</span><span class="mord mathnormal">oc</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">k</span><span class="mspace"> </span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mspace"> </span><span class="mord mathnormal">e</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.01968em;">l</span><span class="mord mathnormal">se</span><span class="mspace"> </span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mord mathnormal">St</span><span class="mord mathnormal">m</span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span><span class="mspace"> </span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mspace"> </span><span class="mord mathnormal">ϵ</span></span></span></span></span></p>
